00:00:00.360 --> 00:00:02.920
This is a video showing my zero dps cdr support monk build.

00:00:03.160 --> 00:00:05.380
The following gears are used for this particular set-up.

00:00:05.840 --> 00:00:06.840
The Laws of Seph

00:00:06.840 --> 00:00:08.740
This provides a major source for spirit regeneration.

00:00:10.080 --> 00:00:11.720
Ashaera's 3p, which is optional.

00:00:13.340 --> 00:00:15.180
Ring of Royal Grandeur. Compulsory.

00:00:17.440 --> 00:00:19.380
The Fist of Az'Turrasq. Compulsory

00:00:19.380 --> 00:00:21.620
But you still can play the build if you don't have it yet.

00:00:24.060 --> 00:00:25.840
Captain Crimson's 2p. Compulsory.

00:00:29.480 --> 00:00:30.780
Born's 2p. Compulsory.

00:00:32.580 --> 00:00:34.080
Halcyon's Ascent. Recommended.

00:00:35.220 --> 00:00:36.760
Strongarm Bracers. Recommended.

00:00:37.820 --> 00:00:40.220
Stone of Jordan with physical damage. Recommended.

00:00:44.620 --> 00:00:46.780
The Furnace. Recommended to swap this for bosses.

00:00:47.300 --> 00:00:49.460
BK's Wedding Band. Swap this for bosses.

00:00:51.480 --> 00:00:52.980
The core stats for this build are:

00:00:52.980 --> 00:00:53.980
Cooldown reduction.

00:00:53.980 --> 00:00:56.320
This has the highest priority and you need to stack as much as you can.

00:00:56.320 --> 00:00:57.320
Health globe healing bonus.

00:00:57.320 --> 00:00:59.600
This improves Epiphany: Soothing Mist healing effect.

00:01:00.040 --> 00:01:02.540
+phys/elite damage for improving explosion damage from Exploding Palm.

00:01:02.860 --> 00:01:05.580
Defensive stats including armor, resistance and vitality etc.

00:01:05.580 --> 00:01:07.260
Resource cost reduction and attack speed allow you to spam more palms.

00:01:07.260 --> 00:01:08.760
Critical chance and damage are not needed.

00:01:09.260 --> 00:01:10.580
Now let's have some action.

00:01:10.840 --> 00:01:14.480
This build focuses on cooldown reduction and maximizing group support,

00:01:14.480 --> 00:01:18.360
including various damage buffs, damage reduction, and healing.

00:01:18.360 --> 00:01:19.360
The following skills are used:

00:01:20.060 --> 00:01:22.040
Inner Sanctuary: Forbidden City.

00:01:22.320 --> 00:01:24.020
Cyclone Strike: Implosion.

00:01:24.340 --> 00:01:26.140
Mantra of Conviction: Annihilation.

00:01:26.420 --> 00:01:28.740
The rune gives movement speed between fights.

00:01:29.080 --> 00:01:30.980
Epiphany: Soothing Mist.

00:01:31.040 --> 00:01:36.240
With maximal CDR and HGHB, this consistently provides the group with enormous amount of healing.

00:01:36.240 --> 00:01:39.240
Left click. Exploding Palm: Flesh is Weak.

00:01:39.700 --> 00:01:42.420
Right click. Blinding Flash: Self Reflection.

00:01:42.740 --> 00:01:44.800
This provides consistent crowd control,

00:01:44.800 --> 00:01:47.020
neuralize most of the melee damage source,

00:01:47.200 --> 00:01:49.800
and constantly interrupt elite/bosses spell casting.

00:01:50.360 --> 00:01:52.040
The basic rotation of the skills are:

00:01:52.040 --> 00:01:53.040
Pull with CS, 

00:01:53.540 --> 00:01:55.860
blind enemies and drop Inner Sanctuary,

00:01:56.300 --> 00:01:57.300
spam EP, 

00:01:57.500 --> 00:01:59.380
teammates triggers the chain explosion,

00:01:59.580 --> 00:02:00.580
move on to the next pack.

00:02:01.260 --> 00:02:02.900
The passive abilities use here are:

00:02:02.900 --> 00:02:04.760
One with Everything. Compulsory.

00:02:04.980 --> 00:02:06.480
Resolve. Recommended.

00:02:06.700 --> 00:02:08.920
Beacon of Ytar. Compulsory.

00:02:09.080 --> 00:02:11.200
Fleet Footed. Recommended.

00:02:12.380 --> 00:02:17.360
In summary, this set-up of zero dps build provides the basic utility of an EP pulling monk.

00:02:17.640 --> 00:02:21.360
In addition, the build provides the team with a substantial amount of support,

00:02:21.440 --> 00:02:26.680
including damage buffs, damage reduction, movement speed, crowd control, and healing.

00:02:26.680 --> 00:02:27.400
Thanks for watching.

00:02:27.400 --> 00:02:30.020
And I hope you can find the information in this video useful.

